title: Classic Self Improvement Books
description:
Being Shunned as an EXJW can leave you without the tools to function in normal society. Here are some classics that served me well:

How to Win Friends & Influence People - Dale Carnegie

The 7 Habits of Highly Effective People - Stephen R Covey

Think and Grow Rich - Napoleon Hill

Malcolm Gladwell -

Outliers

Blink - The Power of Thinking Without Thinking

The Tipping Point

David & Goliath - Underdogs, Misfits & the Art of Battling Giants
